CDC guidelines: People are considered fully vaccinated for COVID-19 ≥2 weeks after they have received the 2nd dose in a 2-dose series (#Pfizer or #Moderna), or ≥2 weeks after they have received a single-dose #vaccine (J&J/Janssen ).
